ncursed-tanks
=============

ncursed-tanks is a game written in C using ncurses interface.
This solution gives a user capability to run it on all *nix platforms.

Usage
-----
Run compiled 'menu' or 'game'.
'Menu' is used to set up a game in user-friendly interface
which then runs 'game' with neccessary command options.
If you want to go straight to the game run 'game' specifing
options or config file.

Gameplay
--------
Gameplay is explained in 'doc/game'.

Dependencies
------------
##make
> Build managemen tool
https://www.gnu.org/software/make/

##ncurses
> Free software emulation of curses
http://www.gnu.org/software/ncurses/ncurses.html

Optional dependencies
---------------------
##doxygen
> Standard tool for generating documentation
http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen/
